  "logNo": "220502839842",
  "title": "오래간만에 회식",
  "addDate": "2015. 10. 8.",
  "categoryNo": "43",
  "parentCategoryNo": "1",
  "url": "https://blog.naver.com/PostView.naver?blogId=isuhani&logNo=220502839842",
  "html_size": 184250,
  "body": "<div id=\"post-view220502839842\" class=\"post-view pcol2 _param(1) _postViewArea220502839842\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div style=\"font-size:10pt; font-family:'957317_10';\" class=\"view\"><p>어제는 수요일이라 3시까지 진료를 마치고</p><p>한의원 대청소를 했어요</p><p><br /></p><p>필요없는 물건들은 버리고, </p><p>여기 닦고 저기 닦고 </p><p>먼지도 닦고..</p><p><br /></p><p>한의원이&nbsp;공기가 더 깨끗해졌어요</p><p><br /></p><p>약간의 변화를 주기위해</p><p>소파 위치도 살짝 바꿔주고 ㅎㅎㅎ</p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p>그리고 그 후,</p><p>우리 한의원 식구들끼리 오래간만에 회식을 하러 갔답니다 ^^</p><p><br /></p><p>아이 좋아라~</p><p><br /></p><p><a href=\"http://m.gfmarket.naver.com/sticker/detail/code/moon_and_james\" target=\"_blank\"\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/153506a21da04ec6.png\" alt=\"moon_and_james-3\"></a></p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p>그래서 간곳은 이수역 근처에 있는 장어식당</p><p><br /></p><p>장어식당이니까 당연히 1번&nbsp;메뉴는 장어구요 ㅋㅋ</p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/27dc5577e1fa95eb.jpg\" width=\"480\" height=\"360\" style=\"cursor: pointer;border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); rheight: 360px; rwidth: 480px;\" id=\"20151008_85/isuhani_1444268045993ujxAA_JPEG/1.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_000000000000003356FE5222')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/27dc5577e1fa95eb.jpg\"></p><p>&#8203;</p><p><br /></p><p>일단 장어를 불판에 곱게 올려준다요</p><p>&#8203;</p><p><br /></p><p><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/d539c1c3d459081b.jpg\" width=\"480\" height=\"360\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rheight: 360px; rwidth: 480px;\" id=\"20151008_176/isuhani_1444268006198uY6Q7_JPEG/2.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_000000000000003356FE5222')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/d539c1c3d459081b.jpg\"></p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p>앞뒤로 잘익어가는 장어는 먹기 좋은 크기로 이쁘게 잘라주고</p><p>&#8203;</p><p>&#8203;</p><p><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/1cd61625a733d0ed.jpg\" width=\"480\" height=\"360\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rheight: 360px; rwidth: 480px;\" id=\"20151008_131/isuhani_1444268006407y2teA_JPEG/3.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_000000000000003356FE5222')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/1cd61625a733d0ed.jpg\"></p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p>타지 않게 잘 뒤집어 줘야합니다 </p><p>&#8203;</p><p>&#8203;</p><p><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/0b449e8c75483793.jpg\" width=\"480\" height=\"360\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rheight: 360px; rwidth: 480px;\" id=\"20151008_63/isuhani_1444268006599qVlvF_JPEG/4.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_000000000000003356FE5222')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/0b449e8c75483793.jpg\"></p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p>이제 다익어서 조금씩 타고 있네요 ㅜㅜ</p><p>얼른 먹어야지~</p><p>&#8203;</p><p>&#8203;</p><p><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/ff19405e5b0347a4.jpg\" width=\"480\" height=\"640\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rheight: 640px; rwidth: 480px;\" id=\"20151008_83/isuhani_1444268006805B6BSc_JPEG/5.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_000000000000003356FE5222')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/ff19405e5b0347a4.jpg\"></p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p>장어 한점 집어서 양념소스에 살짝 찍구 쌈장과 고추를 함께 더해주면....</p><p>&#8203;</p><p>&#8203;</p><p><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/c9b81efd8f40cf72.jpg\" width=\"480\" height=\"640\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rheight: 640px; rwidth: 480px;\" id=\"20151008_253/isuhani_1444268007098QefDo_JPEG/6.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_000000000000003356FE5222')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/c9b81efd8f40cf72.jpg\"></p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p>잠깐! 입에 들어가기 전에 한번더 찍구!!!</p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p>아 맛있다!! </p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p>맛있게 먹는 모습을 찍었어야는데, 먹느라 바빠서 음식사진밖에 못찍었네요 ㅜ ㅋㅋ</p><p><br /></p><p>아쉬운데로 이모티콘으로 대신하겠습니다 </p><p><a href=\"http://m.gfmarket.naver.com/sticker/detail/code/moon_and_james\" target=\"_blank\"\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/be15837a2d144691.png\" width=\"140\" height=\"105\" style=\"width: 140px; height: 105px;\" alt=\"moon_and_james-20\"></a></p><p><br /></p><p>ㅋㅋㅋㅋㅋㅋㅋㅋㅋㅋㅋ</p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p>우리 원장님께서 직접 구워주시니 더 맛있었다요 <img src=\"https://ssl.pstatic.net/static.se2/static/img/emoticon/1_03.gif\" onload=\"setTimeout('utility.resizeImageWithId(\\'static\\/img\\/emoticon\\/1_03.gif\\')',200)\" style=\"cursor: pointer;\" id=\"static/img/emoticon/1_03.gif\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_000000000000003356FE5222')\" alt=\"\"></p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p>그리고 이런 얘기 저런 얘기도 하고</p><p>웃다가 심각해졌다가 ㅋㅋㅋ 그리고 또 웃고.. ㅎㅎㅎ</p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p>오래간만에.. <br /></p><p>한의원 원내말고 식구들끼리 모여서 같이 밖에서도 이런 시간을 보내니&nbsp;기분이 좋네요 ^^</p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p>얘기하다 장어가 없어져서 ㅋㅋㅋㅋㅋ</p><p><br /></p><p>원장님께서 전복회도 시켜주셨어요</p><p>(원장님이랑 선생님들 말씀나누고 계실때 제가 하나씩 다 먹고있었거든요 ㅎㅎㅎ)</p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p>&nbsp;<br style=\"clear: both;\" /><br style=\"clear: both;\" /><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/5f1cb75d1277b8d5.jpg\" width=\"480\" height=\"360\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rheight: 360px; rwidth: 480px;\" id=\"20151008_284/isuhani_1444268007314pNnXG_JPEG/7.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_000000000000003356FE5222')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/5f1cb75d1277b8d5.jpg\"></p><p><br /></p><p>요거 전복회는 처음 먹어보는데, </p><p>고소한 참기름이랑 소금과 함께 먹으니&nbsp;너무 맛있네요~&nbsp;</p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p>이렇게 맛있는것도 먹고 즐거운시간도 보내고.. 좋다~</p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p>앞으로도 이런 즐거운 시간 자주 했으면 좋겠다요 ㅎㅎ</p></div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>",
